Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.72,0:00:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Needs more of a beat...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.06,0:00:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll up the tempo a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.15,0:00:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.98,0:00:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The drums set the rhythm,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.19,0:00:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the melody stimulates your ears\Nas the lyrics burst out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That moment you realize deep down\Nthat this is what you've been looking for...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's as if my heart's about to burst,\Nready to leap into the sky!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.84,0:00:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Already midnight...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.47,0:01:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait!!\NWhat am I even doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.18,0:01:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to study! Study! STUDY!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.90,0:01:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Overlapping these just feels off...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.03,0:01:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Maybe if I lower this a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.21,0:01:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,STUDY, DAMMIT!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,3: UNORTHODOX PROBLEMS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.98,0:03:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!! Focus!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.94,0:03:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.57,0:03:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The pigeon was on the rhythm...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Focus!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm still on the same page as yesterday...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.00,0:03:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like I wasted an entire day!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An acoustic song...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.46,0:03:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did Momoka-san have an acoustic guitar as well...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Nina-chan! Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you eaten yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah- not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got buns! Hot! Steamed! Buns!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.48,0:03:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just bad manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,See? You're a real rich kid, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.11,0:03:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sauce? On buns?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's tasty, trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I got these from a friend at school,\Nwho had some spares from her job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.37,0:04:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.71,0:04:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice. I'm glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- So, about that song...\N- Oh, is it ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- If only it were that easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- Really? Then why did you make me come?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't exactly live next door, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.14,0:04:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to talk about what type of song we want to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, I'm struggling to see what would best suit us three.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I get to jam on the drums I'm good with anything, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And you, Nina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.28,0:04:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If I recall, I showed you this app like a week ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:05:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And you already made something like this?\NYou're incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... Momoka-san told me that with this
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I could write songs by feel than by music sheets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So I gave it a try...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.26,0:05:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, to have gotten {\i1}this{\i0} good...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.22,0:05:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You must've spent like 8 hours a day on it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'e you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.53,0:05:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to study! STUDY!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.45,0:05:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san! Didn't I already tell you that I've got no time for this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.87,0:05:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially with my exams coming up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know, then don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,B-but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the one who showed you the app.\NI'll uninstall it, so just focus on singing-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, you can keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Make up your mind then!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.97,0:05:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need to balance both activities, while Momoka-san takes care of the band. Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.23,0:06:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you talking to...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.65,0:06:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,To MYSELF!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye. See you next practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear, what's her deal? I can never figure her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. I'll head home too then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah wait, I've still got some buns...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have them all. See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.75,0:06:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.67,0:06:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna walk to the station together?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, you're incredible.\NTo write a song out of nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... I just cobbled together some pre-existing sounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But the one who needs to come up with the lyrics is you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,S-sorry, I need to head to the store real quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.87,0:06:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,O-oh no... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.54,0:07:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thought I'd head home by foot, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Go yourself! ...uh, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Got my shift at work after this. Can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I can't... not do it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina! It's okay if it's after school,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but just get it back to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it for the buns!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, I'm seeing it in person...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be a bumpkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Which way?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Eeehm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:07:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.77,0:08:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.04,0:08:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehm... Is A-awa-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Awa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! You mean Subaru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's good enough as is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wah! Nina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it hard getting here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had told me where your school is, I would've come for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry {\i0}for the delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.44,0:08:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.65,0:08:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you forgot it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:08:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm such a klutz!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:08:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Everyone's waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- Got it.\N- See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're free now, right?\NWanna grab a bite? Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll treat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I... have to study... so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. What about this weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Like say, Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, you don't need to worry. I was just doing a favor...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.93,0:09:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Right then... I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.10,0:09:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be better for you if I quit the band?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not an idiot, you know. I can tell you're avoiding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.41,0:09:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh... no, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I don't want to get in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's other bands I could join.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.45,0:09:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You've got it wrong! That's not what I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.21,0:09:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:09:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I mean, I can always study later...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I guess that was just an excuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.48,0:10:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant about me, not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.77,0:10:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I started music club when I was in middle school, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's not like I'm that good at it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Being in a band means you're someone who\Ncan't cut it on their own,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,so it can often end up a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have conflicting opinions,\Nyou can't keep them to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if you just care about keeping appearances,\Nsomething's bound to go wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So if there's something you're not happy with, I say out with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.42,0:10:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No... it's not that I'm not happy with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop being such a broken record.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's going to hate me anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Focus! That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I just... distance myself from everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.44,0:10:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And then that leads people to try and get closer with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? And what's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing wrong, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:11:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that when someone tries to get friendly with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.95,0:11:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,"You really thought it'd work out?"\N"As if I could have it this easy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...I keep having those thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.62,0:11:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, what a pain you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.12,0:11:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That why you quit school too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it. It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Where did you hear that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be nice, the view from that high horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.93,0:11:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You know nothing about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so you know, even if I am going to acting school,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.52,0:11:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that doesn't mean I'm bound to get a degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the same in that regard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so! You want to be an actress, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.11,0:11:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That means you've got a dream to chase after!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You've at least got something to pride yourself on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I said that you don't know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know who she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I get the feeling I've seen her before...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Detective Grandma on the Case{\i0}.\NRebrodacasts every afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my actual grandma though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She won't ever shut up about how I've gotta follow in her footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.22,0:12:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She said I was going to acting school or she'd kick me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you don't want to be an actress...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And you continue going to acting school...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. And I hate myself for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why keep doing something\NI'm not interested in?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, those around me don't see it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.78,0:12:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone says it's just natural for me to follow in my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why a band then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's my modest way to rebel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since middle school I didn't want to end up in the acting club, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I liked bands, I joined the music club.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.84,0:12:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Gave it a shot and had a blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I even ended up forming a band in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Your grandmother doesn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No way I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.89,0:12:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way! Seen Hachiko yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't we gonna look like bumpkins?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:12:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So what? You're the real deal after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If I feel like talking, I'll make you hang out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on you're my bestie Nina! You dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Girls Band Cry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}SUNDAY NOON
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A street show?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Thought it'd be a good place to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.25,0:13:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already booked a place for the weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't we agree to finish making a song first?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's obviously still the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, I wanted to get a feel for a show...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...and for the three of us.\N- With a show?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw the pic you took together...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...you come off like a cocktail of tension and unease.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- Rude.\N- I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's exactly why I called out to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That goes for both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- What do you think, Nina? \N- It's all too sudden, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...I might get what she means.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, can we really throw a show without a bassist?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't play anything, right Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.38,0:14:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax, it's just a local event. We'll manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I've got this bad boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.42,0:14:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A looper.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You feed it sound just like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.02,0:14:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.52,0:14:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehm... when you say "street show", surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mean performing in front of people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.65,0:14:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What else? I mean, didn't we meet at a street sho-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where do you think you're going? \N- Home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go! I wasn't told any of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Pipe down! You sang at the station, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.59,0:14:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you say that, I'm not going!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.22,0:14:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can pull that off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. If anything happens, I'll cover up for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then shouldn't you be singing, Momoka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:14:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're so much better than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, wanna do guitar then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I can't play it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.61,0:15:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you already. I want you as our vocalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.32,0:15:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get it when you sing. Trust in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.29,0:15:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you don't mind quitting the band?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.88,0:15:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cheating, forcing me to leave the band!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What kinda logic is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- But I mean, I--\N- Stop chickening out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you kill it or suck at it,\Nsucceed or fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.49,0:15:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you're gonna have regrets eitherway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's....\N- ...the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So just take all you're feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.66,0:16:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and pour all of it into singing your heart out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.37,0:16:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.83,0:16:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Match point! It's Nina's loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.67,0:16:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru-chan, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.25,0:16:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn that anger into music!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.96,0:16:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what makes you who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, they've got some sweet gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Though really, it's just that they're the chepest too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see, let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, pretty sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, do you have the song we made before memorized?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to include a bit of the song you made on the app.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.67,0:16:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's give it a shot then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why else do you think we're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't so suddenly...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.09,0:16:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I told you, stop chickening out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's practice. Doesn't matter if it turns out good or bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.22,0:16:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're bound to fail anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:16:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,More slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.72,0:17:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One, two, three, four.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.86,0:17:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:17:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I got goosebumps...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So many goosebumps!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.08,0:18:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You fell straight into Momoka-san's trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you've had a taste, there's no more going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But... why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, human bodies...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...react to the electric waves of music\Nand can't help but dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Singing and dancing is hard-coded into our DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing, just happy to see you like this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I also got goosebumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.86,0:18:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, gimme a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.94,0:18:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A regular with a beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.65,0:18:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A regular, without the onions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.28,0:18:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A regular...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.58,0:18:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you hungover?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the ones who told me to sing my heart out...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because no one can sing like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up already...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Th...thenks fur the mealll..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:19:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you'll get your voice back,\N by tomorrow, so go easy on it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.59,0:19:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a band?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.26,0:19:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed the guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're up for it, come see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.73,0:19:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}SHIN-KAWASAKI (TENTATIVE)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.90,0:19:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...so she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.65,0:19:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking we could tell them about us too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.24,0:19:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, gotta bounce.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.16,0:19:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, she treated us both today too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,To gyuudon, and the karaoke too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.60,0:19:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are Momoka-san's former bandmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.10,0:19:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.86,0:20:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now then, our next band is having their very first debut!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A female trio from Kawasaki!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.53,0:20:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Make some noise for...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}..."Shin-Kawasaki" ?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.79,0:20:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We need a good talk later. And a better name.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I already told you, it's just tentative.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry for being late.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't tell me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.22,0:20:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...that's your stage outfit?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.89,0:20:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it no good?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.39,0:20:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like I told you, you gotta bare your heart naked.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.31,0:20:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go get changed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ehm. Testing, testing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nina, I thought it'd be best if you wore something you wouldn't like.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.74,0:20:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't think about it too hard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.50,0:20:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just throw your emotions out there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't panic. I'm here with you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:20:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nina, you're a spineless coward.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.13,0:21:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One who can't believe in herself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're like a big ball of self-inflicted complexes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That a compliment?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.01,0:21:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on Nina! It's our turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.73,0:21:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All that energy and emotion you've accumulated...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.35,0:21:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's... what we call rock.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.86,0:21:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No one knows who you are.\NNo one cares who you are.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.13,0:21:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But doesn't that make it more fun?.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.86,0:22:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina... let's Rock'n'Roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.74,0:22:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If nothing changes\Nno matter how long I wait{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.66,0:22:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then there's no one who'll reach out to me, no one to care{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.03,0:22:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not as if the pain disappears\Nwhen you blame someone else{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.87,0:22:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I pray to say goodbye\Nto these cowering days{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.63,0:22:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}While my knees are all the way up to my chest{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.09,0:22:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I don't believe in no God\Nwho'd abandon me like this{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.51,0:22:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- {\i1}Shut the hell up!\N{\i0}- {\i1}(Shut the hell up!){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.64,0:22:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- {\i1}Leave me alone!\N{\i0}- {\i1}Leave me alone!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.14,0:22:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A stranger I don't even know\Nis singing me a song{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.73,0:22:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}telling me with all their voice that I'm not alone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I'm sure some souls would be saved\Nwith just those words alone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.44,0:22:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I don't know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.24,0:22:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or do I?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.57,0:22:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that so?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.70,0:22:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I forgot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.03,0:22:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a pain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.20,0:22:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanna break.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.49,0:22:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've got no courage left!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.50,0:23:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Someone hurry up and tell me\Na reason to live{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.13,0:23:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After all, there's many that could just replace who I am{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.42,0:23:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can't just tell me to be myself, it's not that easy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.72,0:23:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Take it back if it's for granted{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.64,0:23:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the end, I really am\Nbursting with dreams{\i0}
